WEBVTT

NOTE Video ID: sUh3F6VvoBM

NOTE Language: en

00:15:35.100 --> 00:15:40.260
I bow to all the seekers of truth.

00:15:45.940 --> 00:15:49.180
Can you hear her there – all the way?

00:15:59.100 --> 00:16:05.220
Or you may use this. Better. I will just speak. All right.

00:16:12.740 --> 00:16:20.940
I’m very grateful to the Sahaja yogis of Vienna,

00:16:21.860 --> 00:16:25.340
who have invited Me to this place,

00:16:25.660 --> 00:16:30.780
and this is My first visit to Vienna.

00:16:41.660 --> 00:16:48.060
This is the last state that I had to touch in Europe

00:16:48.620 --> 00:16:52.940
and so I must say, lot of work has been already done

00:16:53.380 --> 00:16:57.860
in Sahaja Yoga in other countries.

00:16:58.540 --> 00:17:01.940
Somehow it happened that I had to come to Vienna

00:17:02.380 --> 00:17:05.340
after such a long time.

00:17:14.700 --> 00:17:17.780
I’m really very happy to see there are so many

00:17:18.100 --> 00:17:22.220
seekers in Vienna.

00:17:26.140 --> 00:17:29.180
And they are the seekers of truth.

00:17:33.860 --> 00:17:39.060
But first of all, we have to understand what is truth.

00:17:43.220 --> 00:17:47.180
Whatever truth we have so far as human beings,

00:17:47.660 --> 00:17:50.980
has been known to us through our awareness,

00:17:51.300 --> 00:17:54.980
through our central nervous system.

00:18:00.660 --> 00:18:03.220
For example, if you see the flowers, the flowers are white;

00:18:03.500 --> 00:18:08.500
we can see they are there - this is the truth for us.

00:18:11.460 --> 00:18:15.700
I touch this steel and I know it is cold, so I know it

00:18:16.060 --> 00:18:22.740
is steel and I know it is cold - is a fact with My fingers.

00:18:26.500 --> 00:18:30.980
It is not any imagination or a mental projection to think

00:18:31.340 --> 00:18:36.540
that this is the flute of Shri Krishna.

00:18:45.460 --> 00:18:51.380
Because I can see, I can hear and I can feel that I know

00:18:51.820 --> 00:18:55.300
this is the truth, because I know through My experiences

00:18:55.700 --> 00:18:59.660
of the central nervous system.

00:19:04.620 --> 00:19:07.460
In My own awareness as a human being I know

00:19:07.860 --> 00:19:12.100
there is fragrance in the flowers.

00:19:14.700 --> 00:19:20.060
In My own understanding I know the aesthetics of this place.

00:19:24.060 --> 00:19:27.260
If you take a horse through a dirty lane,

00:19:27.580 --> 00:19:33.580
he doesn’t feel the dirt and filth and the smell of that place.

00:19:40.620 --> 00:19:43.740
But a human being, when he passes through those lanes,

00:19:44.180 --> 00:19:46.420
he knows that it’s dirty, he can’t bear it,

00:19:46.860 --> 00:19:50.220
because his awareness is such.

00:19:57.060 --> 00:20:00.140
This is the difference of awareness in our evolution

00:20:00.500 --> 00:20:05.380
that we have achieved as human beings.

00:20:08.580 --> 00:20:12.140
So, one has to know that whatever is going to happen to us

00:20:12.540 --> 00:20:16.820
has to happen in our awareness.

00:20:21.860 --> 00:20:26.220
That whatever we achieve or whatever we get in our

00:20:26.460 --> 00:20:28.900
central nervous system is absolutely logical and

00:20:29.300 --> 00:20:33.580
can be experimented with.

00:20:38.300 --> 00:20:42.060
That we can verify it.

00:20:43.060 --> 00:20:48.660
It is not like a dark lane that you move on for years together.

00:20:49.100 --> 00:20:54.540
It’s not like a dark lane, dark lane, dark –

00:20:57.780 --> 00:21:02.820
but is an enlightened path where you are aware

00:21:03.060 --> 00:21:07.420
of the higher capacities of human beings.

00:21:11.340 --> 00:21:16.220
What is the higher capacity of a saint?

00:21:18.980 --> 00:21:21.980
It is not that the kind of dress he wears or the way

00:21:22.260 --> 00:21:25.260
he moves about.

00:21:27.340 --> 00:21:32.700
But the higher capacity of a saint is that he is collectively

00:21:33.060 --> 00:21:35.740
conscious.

00:21:40.620 --> 00:21:43.620
Because he’s connected with the Spirit,

00:21:43.940 --> 00:21:48.620
which is a collective being within us.

00:21:54.220 --> 00:21:58.220
So that something has to happen in your awareness

00:21:58.580 --> 00:22:01.580
that you should become, again I say become -

00:22:01.980 --> 00:22:08.140
actualize the experience of collective consciousness.

00:22:15.620 --> 00:22:19.180
Like Mohammad Sahib has clearly said that,

00:22:19.620 --> 00:22:24.980
“In the resurrection time your hands will speak.”

00:22:30.740 --> 00:22:36.300
That He said that you can feel in your hands – what hands

00:22:36.660 --> 00:22:40.060
are going to speak, there’s not going to be any lips here –

00:22:40.420 --> 00:22:42.140
but you are going to feel something in your hands

00:22:42.460 --> 00:22:46.580
which is going to speak for you.

00:22:50.940 --> 00:22:54.140
Now, when we come to truth,

00:22:54.700 --> 00:22:59.500
we have to know about its other alternatives

00:22:59.860 --> 00:23:03.100
and the fakeness of it.

00:23:08.620 --> 00:23:13.740
Every truth can be faked.

00:23:16.860 --> 00:23:19.340
Every flower which is living

00:23:19.660 --> 00:23:23.580
can be made into plastic flowers.

00:23:28.060 --> 00:23:30.940
And to make plastic flower is very easy,

00:23:31.260 --> 00:23:35.620
you can make them by thousands.

00:23:40.820 --> 00:23:46.060
But the real flowers are rare and are real because

00:23:46.420 --> 00:23:53.420
they’re actual flowers living on a living force of life.

00:24:01.460 --> 00:24:07.060
So the evolution is the living process of the living God.

00:24:13.260 --> 00:24:16.700
If that is the truth, then we must understand that

00:24:16.980 --> 00:24:20.380
whatever has happened to us so far in our evolution

00:24:20.380 --> 00:24:22.580
spontaneously, in the same way

00:24:22.820 --> 00:24:27.380
something has to happen to us, spontaneously.

00:24:38.060 --> 00:24:41.300
Like a seed, if it has to sprout,

00:24:41.540 --> 00:24:43.380
you have to put it in the Mother Earth because

00:24:43.860 --> 00:24:48.500
She has the quality, She has the authority to germinate it.

00:24:58.580 --> 00:25:03.220
Do we pay money to the seed to sprout?

00:25:05.780 --> 00:25:10.180
How can you pay for God?

00:25:12.340 --> 00:25:16.060
I can’t understand the naiveness of the Western people

00:25:16.340 --> 00:25:19.300
not to understand that you cannot pay to someone

00:25:19.580 --> 00:25:25.980
who thinks that he can deliver the spiritual life to you.

00:25:35.420 --> 00:25:37.900
These are all parasites,

00:25:37.900 --> 00:25:40.700
and if you want to have parasites as your guru,

00:25:40.980 --> 00:25:42.460
you go ahead with it.

00:25:42.700 --> 00:25:44.220
Nobody can control you in there,

00:25:44.220 --> 00:25:47.540
because you have the freedom.

00:25:55.780 --> 00:25:59.820
The other school of thought which is revolting against

00:26:00.140 --> 00:26:03.940
this kind of fakeness could be that they are all fake,

00:26:04.260 --> 00:26:09.500
that’s all falsehood, there’s no truth – that’s also wrong.

00:26:16.820 --> 00:26:19.100
So many people who have gone through the

00:26:20.060 --> 00:26:23.180
circus of guru-shopping come to end that

00:26:23.500 --> 00:26:26.780
we should become communists now.

00:26:35.220 --> 00:26:38.260
That is also another extreme.

00:26:39.500 --> 00:26:42.620
That’s a denial of the truth.

00:26:44.820 --> 00:26:48.580
So it is in the center there is the truth, no doubt about it,

00:26:48.820 --> 00:26:54.660
but it is not a thing that you can purchase in the market.

00:27:02.780 --> 00:27:06.460
Specially in the West people are pampered,

00:27:06.740 --> 00:27:09.220
their ego is pampered, if you can pay for something

00:27:09.220 --> 00:27:10.700
or you can purchase something,

00:27:11.060 --> 00:27:13.980
you can possess something.

00:27:21.820 --> 00:27:26.060
But I said, “You cannot pay for God.”

00:27:29.580 --> 00:27:32.060
Anybody who takes money in the name of God

00:27:32.340 --> 00:27:36.500
and lives upon it is a parasite.

00:27:40.820 --> 00:27:45.860
And the one who is a parasite cannot be your guru,

00:27:46.260 --> 00:27:47.500
he is much less than you;

00:27:47.820 --> 00:27:51.740
you won’t live like a parasite yourself.

00:27:58.780 --> 00:28:00.420
And the second point I told you,

00:28:00.780 --> 00:28:02.620
when it is a living process within you,

00:28:03.380 --> 00:28:08.140
then you must know that you cannot put in any effort.

00:28:21.780 --> 00:28:26.460
Is a simple thing of a flower becoming a fruit.

00:28:29.580 --> 00:28:32.060
Now you jump before it or stand on your head

00:28:32.260 --> 00:28:33.980
or take out your clothes or wear any clothes –

00:28:34.300 --> 00:28:37.260
will it become the fruit?

00:28:45.340 --> 00:28:49.060
How much does it take to jump or to change it or to have

00:28:49.420 --> 00:28:54.340
some sort of a nude body, how much does it take?

00:28:58.540 --> 00:29:01.220
Anybody can do that.

00:29:02.340 --> 00:29:04.900
Sahaja Yoga is a path for the true seekers,

00:29:05.180 --> 00:29:07.700
and not for the people who run after fake things

00:29:08.060 --> 00:29:10.860
and do not want to face it.

00:29:17.860 --> 00:29:21.540
It’s a category of people who are men of God,

00:29:21.940 --> 00:29:25.620
who are seeking the Truth, and who do not accept

00:29:25.940 --> 00:29:30.060
anything that is fake.

00:29:36.580 --> 00:29:41.220
And is a category of courageous people,

00:29:43.540 --> 00:29:49.460
the brave people, who can discard all that is a hang-up

00:29:49.900 --> 00:29:53.900
or a conditioning on them.

00:29:54.380 --> 00:29:58.420
Who can discard, who can give up.

00:30:06.980 --> 00:30:11.540
So, God has given you everything.

00:30:14.060 --> 00:30:18.220
While making you a human being, in His gentle care,

00:30:18.700 --> 00:30:21.660
He has created you a beautiful human being

00:30:21.900 --> 00:30:25.340
and all the roots are within you.

00:30:34.180 --> 00:30:39.300
Now, when you try to put in your effort to find God,

00:30:39.780 --> 00:30:43.980
then you are not spontaneous.

00:30:49.780 --> 00:30:53.060
It’s all man-made.

00:30:54.100 --> 00:30:59.820
And in that effort you start moving to the left or to the right.

00:31:05.300 --> 00:31:07.940
Tomorrow I will tell you in details about the left side

00:31:08.260 --> 00:31:10.540
and the right side, but today I will just tell you that

00:31:10.940 --> 00:31:13.980
when you move to the left, you fall into the trap of your

00:31:14.300 --> 00:31:19.220
subconscious or into the collective subconscious.

00:31:34.700 --> 00:31:37.580
In Sanskrit it is called as Adi Bhautik.

00:31:38.060 --> 00:31:41.060
Adi Bhautik.

00:31:42.380 --> 00:31:44.580
Bhautik.

00:31:45.060 --> 00:31:50.500
Means it is the collective subconscious within us.

00:31:52.300 --> 00:31:56.620
You get drawn into it and you start getting lost and

00:31:56.940 --> 00:32:01.540
completely mesmerized and brainwashed.

00:32:09.740 --> 00:32:13.060
If you are given an ego trip on the right-hand side,

00:32:13.300 --> 00:32:16.740
you can fall a trip to that also.

00:32:28.780 --> 00:32:33.340
Human beings accept conditionings very fast.

00:32:38.820 --> 00:32:41.060
conditionings

00:32:49.620 --> 00:32:56.220
There was an experiment with twenty people in England.

00:32:57.060 --> 00:33:01.100
They told ten people to behave like prisoners

00:33:01.660 --> 00:33:05.420
and ten people to behave like jailers.

00:33:17.340 --> 00:33:20.060
They were just told that, “It’s a drama, you have to be

00:33:20.380 --> 00:33:22.060
there for a month and we want to see

00:33:22.380 --> 00:33:26.260
if there is any change in your behavior.”

00:33:31.740 --> 00:33:33.300
And they were told again and again,

00:33:33.740 --> 00:33:38.540
“It’s an enactment, it’s not reality, it’s just enactment.”

00:33:43.340 --> 00:33:47.060
But, when they went into the jail, the jailers became

00:33:47.460 --> 00:33:50.580
very arrogant and egoistical, and the prisoners

00:33:50.900 --> 00:33:52.860
became absolutely slavish and going through all the

00:33:53.380 --> 00:33:59.260
hardships which these ego-oriented people poured on them.

00:34:18.420 --> 00:34:21.460
Out of the twenty, only one revolted against this

00:34:21.820 --> 00:34:24.500
because he was beaten up by these so-called jailers

00:34:24.900 --> 00:34:29.060
who were acting, actually beaten up.

00:34:35.180 --> 00:34:39.300
And they came out of the jail and they were surprised

00:34:40.620 --> 00:34:43.740
at their own behavior.

00:34:48.540 --> 00:34:51.340
The prisoners had become so weak that they were

00:34:51.740 --> 00:34:54.780
to be admitted in the hospital for all the tortures

00:34:55.100 --> 00:34:58.380
they had to go through.

00:35:05.700 --> 00:35:09.740
And the other ten became so ego-oriented, perhaps

00:35:10.060 --> 00:35:14.060
they must have joined some political party.

00:35:23.100 --> 00:35:26.300
This is the situation of human beings.

00:35:28.380 --> 00:35:31.100
Now with all this,

00:35:32.420 --> 00:35:36.300
the masters of evil geniuses –

00:35:37.060 --> 00:35:39.900
they come as fake gurus.

00:35:40.460 --> 00:35:45.060
And you are so naive, you play into it.

00:35:52.060 --> 00:35:56.940
They have in control lots of evil spirits with them.

00:36:00.140 --> 00:36:03.540
And they can mesmerize you so well that you’ll do all

00:36:03.860 --> 00:36:09.620
kinds of stupid things whatever they want you to do.

00:36:13.900 --> 00:36:17.180
So they make their money, they have women,

00:36:17.620 --> 00:36:22.660
they drink, they enjoy the life more than any king or

00:36:23.140 --> 00:36:28.260
president or any rich man of the world.

00:36:35.140 --> 00:36:39.140
While the poor disciples are finished with their

00:36:39.460 --> 00:36:45.980
all wealth, money, health – they look sickly people.

00:36:49.060 --> 00:36:52.620
One has to know that when you get your realization,

00:36:53.060 --> 00:36:57.420
your own powers must manifest.

00:37:04.660 --> 00:37:07.820
So that you become collectively conscious and that

00:37:08.220 --> 00:37:12.260
you are spirit, manifest the power of that collective

00:37:12.580 --> 00:37:15.580
consciousness.

00:37:23.380 --> 00:37:32.220
Now, the trouble with people is that they are not yet

00:37:32.620 --> 00:37:39.100
know the knowledge of Kundalini in the real sense.

00:37:45.340 --> 00:37:48.340
I have read – I mean, I’ve seen and not read fully –

00:37:48.780 --> 00:37:52.580
but I’ve read some of the books written by Germans

00:37:53.380 --> 00:37:54.940
and by English and by all Western people,

00:37:55.180 --> 00:37:57.180
and I was shocked.

00:37:57.180 --> 00:38:02.700
They had no knowledge about Kundalini.

00:38:12.060 --> 00:38:13.980
Leave alone the Knowledge –

00:38:14.220 --> 00:38:20.900
they had no power from the Divine to awaken the Kundalini.

00:38:25.660 --> 00:38:30.140
They had no character of a saint, which is required

00:38:30.500 --> 00:38:33.260
to raise the Kundalini.

00:38:38.300 --> 00:38:42.300
They were ugly slaves of their greed and lust,

00:38:42.740 --> 00:38:45.100
and they were using this knowledge

00:38:45.500 --> 00:38:48.420
just to make more money.

00:38:57.980 --> 00:39:01.660
Now to understand the basic character of Kundalini,

00:39:03.660 --> 00:39:09.060
one has to know that She is your mother.

00:39:17.980 --> 00:39:22.980
I’m told that German people call their motherland as

00:39:23.340 --> 00:39:31.460
fatherland, but Father is just a spectator of the play.

00:39:39.700 --> 00:39:45.860
Only His Shakti, His power, the Primordial Mother,

00:39:46.180 --> 00:39:51.420
the Holy Ghost does all the job to please this spectator

00:39:51.420 --> 00:39:54.460
who is sitting alone and watching it.

00:40:05.700 --> 00:40:11.060
He resides in your heart as spirit.

00:40:13.740 --> 00:40:17.180
And the Kundalini is the Holy Ghost

00:40:18.220 --> 00:40:21.220
reflected within you.

00:40:27.420 --> 00:40:31.100
The nature of the Kundalini is that She’s the pure,

00:40:33.060 --> 00:40:36.540
ultimate desire.

00:40:41.940 --> 00:40:46.180
This power is called as a residual,

00:40:46.500 --> 00:40:51.420
because it has not yet manifested itself.

00:40:57.420 --> 00:41:03.540
The ultimate desire of every human soul is

00:41:03.900 --> 00:41:08.900
to become the spirit.

00:41:12.100 --> 00:41:13.980
You may do this, you may do that, you may try

00:41:14.340 --> 00:41:17.660
everything – ultimately you will come to the conclusion

00:41:18.060 --> 00:41:23.580
that, “I have not become the spirit.”

00:41:32.700 --> 00:41:35.420
So when you become the spirit, then only

00:41:35.740 --> 00:41:38.780
the manifestation of this Kundalini takes place,

00:41:39.060 --> 00:41:43.100
Her ascent takes place and She is the one who

00:41:43.420 --> 00:41:50.140
creates the position of yoga, the union with the Divine.

00:42:02.340 --> 00:42:05.620
This is the Yoga.

00:42:06.860 --> 00:42:10.260
Also yoga means kaushalam, means the deftness,

00:42:10.700 --> 00:42:16.980
the deftness, how to handle the Kundalini of others,

00:42:17.380 --> 00:42:22.060
the whole knowledge of the divine laws and the divine

00:42:22.420 --> 00:42:30.060
manifestation, is also yoga, is also called kaushalam.

00:42:33.580 --> 00:42:36.820
There are all types of yogas these days prevalent,

00:42:37.140 --> 00:42:41.060
as there are all types of gurus.

00:42:45.620 --> 00:42:49.140
Now the physical yoga is another kind of a thing

00:42:49.500 --> 00:42:56.060
which people think is the ultimate for spiritual life.

00:43:01.300 --> 00:43:03.580
This one comes from Patanjali, who lived

00:43:04.060 --> 00:43:06.860
thousands of years back in India where we had a

00:43:07.100 --> 00:43:10.700
very different system of life.

00:43:15.780 --> 00:43:20.900
Till the age of twenty-five years, the children lived

00:43:21.180 --> 00:43:26.060
in the forest with their realized souls as their gurus.

00:43:33.140 --> 00:43:37.860
There, celibacy was so preserved and innocence

00:43:38.260 --> 00:43:42.380
so respected that a person belonging to the same

00:43:42.620 --> 00:43:46.500
university could not marry each other.

00:43:48.220 --> 00:43:51.620
The same university; the innocence;

00:43:52.620 --> 00:43:54.980
that the students of the same university

00:43:55.420 --> 00:43:58.340
could not marry.

00:44:06.220 --> 00:44:10.940
And these universities were called as gotras.

00:44:13.580 --> 00:44:18.540
Even today, you cannot marry in the same gotra.

00:44:22.860 --> 00:44:25.940
The yama niyama, the vyayama, the one you do

00:44:26.220 --> 00:44:29.900
the exercise, was only done by people who

00:44:30.340 --> 00:44:33.980
were not married,

00:44:37.140 --> 00:44:40.780
according to the need of a particular center

00:44:41.100 --> 00:44:44.580
which was in trouble.

00:44:48.900 --> 00:44:53.620
We too use these exercises wherever it is needed.

00:44:56.940 --> 00:45:01.300
But today’s yoga system which we see is nothing like,

00:45:01.540 --> 00:45:07.300
nothing but taking the whole box of medicine together.

00:45:12.540 --> 00:45:15.340
Without even finding out what is your prakruti, means

00:45:15.580 --> 00:45:18.660
what is your temperament, what is the need of your

00:45:19.100 --> 00:45:22.380
particular body, where is the Kundalini,

00:45:23.060 --> 00:45:26.060
what you have to do to open a particular chakra

00:45:26.340 --> 00:45:30.180
where you are caught up.

00:45:38.620 --> 00:45:42.260
I mean, nobody has that knowledge at all.

00:45:44.420 --> 00:45:47.780
It’s such a mechanical process that has started that

00:45:48.100 --> 00:45:50.780
we all want to be of the same size just like

00:45:51.180 --> 00:45:53.780
a machine thing.

00:45:58.420 --> 00:46:02.220
This one is a very dangerous move because it

00:46:02.780 --> 00:46:07.060
creates problems for the Kundalini to be awakened.

00:46:13.060 --> 00:46:16.980
The people who indulge into too much physical attention,

00:46:17.380 --> 00:46:20.860
and work out too much of physical activities and

00:46:21.100 --> 00:46:25.620
mental activities become futuristic people.

00:46:34.300 --> 00:46:38.740
They become very superficial and dry-tempered.

00:46:40.940 --> 00:46:43.300
With such people there’s a possibility of getting

00:46:43.660 --> 00:46:48.180
people divorced and fighting and quarreling.

00:46:55.100 --> 00:46:58.460
The greatest Hatha yogi which I have known in My life

00:46:58.900 --> 00:47:00.220
was Hitler.

00:47:04.140 --> 00:47:08.340
And he used tantrikas from Tibet to get him

00:47:08.820 --> 00:47:12.500
the power to control the ego of people.

00:47:20.860 --> 00:47:25.500
And he made them so violent that they could not see

00:47:26.900 --> 00:47:31.340
what they were doing.

00:47:36.980 --> 00:47:41.580
There are many gurus who do that way today also.

00:47:44.340 --> 00:47:47.180
They can make you so violent that you cannot see

00:47:47.500 --> 00:47:51.140
what you are doing.

00:47:53.980 --> 00:47:58.100
Or they can make you just cabbages,

00:48:00.060 --> 00:48:08.180
so that you lose all your being and become somebody else.

00:48:11.980 --> 00:48:16.900
But it is done so well that people who do not know

00:48:17.260 --> 00:48:19.580
about the knowledge of Kundalini and spirit

00:48:19.900 --> 00:48:24.140
can be easily captured.

00:48:30.620 --> 00:48:36.980
I call the West as the progress of the shoot,

00:48:37.380 --> 00:48:41.420
of the outside of the tree.

00:48:45.100 --> 00:48:51.340
They know science, politics, economics very well.

00:48:53.660 --> 00:48:58.820
They can create atom bombs to kill themselves.

00:49:00.100 --> 00:49:04.260
They can create even worse things than that.

00:49:04.900 --> 00:49:07.060
They haven’t got the knowledge of the roots on

00:49:07.620 --> 00:49:11.180
which they are growing.

00:49:12.380 --> 00:49:14.820
And the knowledge of the root only can be known

00:49:15.300 --> 00:49:20.380
when you become the spirit, that’s the beginning.

00:49:25.780 --> 00:49:29.180
This is a big disadvantage for the saints who are born

00:49:29.580 --> 00:49:35.580
on this beautiful side of the earth.

00:49:39.380 --> 00:49:43.780
So many seekers are born in the West.

00:49:46.060 --> 00:49:48.900
As the desire of God must have been to give them

00:49:49.260 --> 00:49:53.980
a comfortable life, to get them unemployed, so they

00:49:54.380 --> 00:49:59.500
can be used for God’s employment –

00:50:10.540 --> 00:50:14.060
They got watches to see, to save the time,

00:50:14.260 --> 00:50:17.460
save the time, save the time.

00:50:19.780 --> 00:50:23.820
For what? To go into a pub?

00:50:25.500 --> 00:50:28.620
Or read some horrid books?

00:50:31.140 --> 00:50:36.260
Or waste your life with these horrible gurus?

00:50:37.740 --> 00:50:40.780
So, in the West we have the saints,

00:50:41.620 --> 00:50:45.180
in the East we have the wisdom.

00:50:49.300 --> 00:50:51.580
In the West, people are seeking because

00:50:51.860 --> 00:50:55.260
they are seekers.

00:50:59.540 --> 00:51:02.340
They are a special category of people who are born

00:51:02.740 --> 00:51:05.660
in the West.

00:51:09.220 --> 00:51:11.980
But they lack the basic wisdom to understand

00:51:12.420 --> 00:51:15.540
what is the truth.

00:51:18.820 --> 00:51:22.060
What do we have to achieve?

00:51:23.060 --> 00:51:26.300
What do we have to become?

00:51:27.620 --> 00:51:32.420
This basic wisdom will not be told to you by the people

00:51:32.740 --> 00:51:35.980
who want to make money out of you.

00:51:41.100 --> 00:51:45.860
They want to make a business out of it.

00:51:46.580 --> 00:51:52.900
And thus there’s a big problem for the saints of today.

00:51:55.780 --> 00:52:00.220
As you belong to that area which I call the shoot

00:52:00.580 --> 00:52:03.900
of the tree, people can get enamored by the

00:52:04.180 --> 00:52:07.860
superficial things.

00:52:15.140 --> 00:52:17.820
You can be impressed by somebody who tries

00:52:17.820 --> 00:52:19.940
to pamper your ego.

00:52:26.500 --> 00:52:28.620
pamper, pamper.

00:52:33.460 --> 00:52:37.580
Or could be somebody who dominates you, like Hitler.

00:52:42.060 --> 00:52:46.500
So it is a great responsibility of all the seekers

00:52:46.940 --> 00:52:50.980
in the West to take to wisdom, first of all.

00:52:59.060 --> 00:53:02.700
Logically, you must reach right conclusions.

00:53:11.740 --> 00:53:13.620
right conclusions

00:53:14.060 --> 00:53:20.420
So when it comes to spirituality, you are prepared.

00:53:23.220 --> 00:53:27.380
Supposing I come to Vienna from somewhere lost

00:53:27.700 --> 00:53:30.460
conditions – how will I know this is Vienna,

00:53:30.460 --> 00:53:32.060
unless and until somebody says -

00:53:32.300 --> 00:53:35.300
this is the way to go to Vienna?

00:53:41.620 --> 00:53:44.100
And how will I know it is Vienna because I should

00:53:44.460 --> 00:53:49.220
know what Vienna is like, first of all.

00:53:53.580 --> 00:53:57.940
So, one comes to another conclusion that the

00:53:58.340 --> 00:54:01.380
description of the collective consciousness

00:54:01.940 --> 00:54:04.940
must be already there in the scriptures

00:54:05.260 --> 00:54:09.180
which are written long time back.

00:54:16.740 --> 00:54:20.220
It has to tally with findings of the psychology,

00:54:20.740 --> 00:54:23.860
like Jung psychology.

00:54:26.780 --> 00:54:29.340
It has to tally the many predictions; like thousands

00:54:29.700 --> 00:54:32.140
of years back, there was a book written called

00:54:32.580 --> 00:54:33.900
Nadi Granth

00:54:39.180 --> 00:54:44.860
by Bhrigu, who was the pioneer of our astrology.

00:54:48.700 --> 00:54:52.060
We should find out from other sources like great poets,

00:54:52.380 --> 00:54:55.100
like William Blake, I know English, has clearly written

00:54:55.500 --> 00:54:59.060
about Sahaja Yoga.

00:55:05.140 --> 00:55:08.220
So many such realized people, great people,

00:55:08.580 --> 00:55:11.460
like Dante, you can say, Homer, you can say,

00:55:12.220 --> 00:55:18.060
they have written about Sahaja Yoga in so many ways.

00:55:27.500 --> 00:55:31.500
If we take to all these things, then we know that

00:55:32.180 --> 00:55:35.420
this is Vienna.

00:55:40.100 --> 00:55:43.460
But we should not be brainwashed by people

00:55:43.980 --> 00:55:46.220
who just give us big stories or read some book and

00:55:46.780 --> 00:55:48.540
convert it into some other knowledge and say,

00:55:48.980 --> 00:55:55.140
“This is this, this is this”, and just talk, talk, talk.

00:56:00.900 --> 00:56:06.940
Now the time has come, to become.

00:56:08.860 --> 00:56:11.220
Now the time has come for this divine power

00:56:12.060 --> 00:56:15.620
to manifest itself.

00:56:17.780 --> 00:56:20.980
We see a flower becoming a fruit,

00:56:25.140 --> 00:56:29.220
billions and billions of them in their seasons.

00:56:32.500 --> 00:56:34.820
We see ourselves breathing,

00:56:37.300 --> 00:56:41.140
we see ourselves digesting,

00:56:42.060 --> 00:56:45.420
we don’t pay for it, do we?

00:56:47.180 --> 00:56:50.940
Then who is doing all this?

00:56:51.380 --> 00:56:53.060
Which is that power that is doing?

00:56:53.540 --> 00:56:57.740
We don’t even think about it.

00:57:00.540 --> 00:57:03.820
We just take it for granted.

00:57:04.580 --> 00:57:07.580
Look at these eyes that are made, are the best

00:57:07.900 --> 00:57:13.140
camera that you can think of, so advanced.

00:57:16.180 --> 00:57:19.180
Look at this human body, so great.

00:57:22.180 --> 00:57:28.420
Look at this human brain, so expansive.

00:57:30.740 --> 00:57:36.780
Why all this was made, and who has done it?

00:57:38.860 --> 00:57:44.060
Why we have become human beings from amoeba?

00:57:44.660 --> 00:57:47.660
What is so great about human beings that they are

00:57:48.100 --> 00:57:53.260
the epitome of all the Creation?

00:57:56.580 --> 00:57:59.580
Is it just to sit down and feel guilty about all small

00:57:59.980 --> 00:58:03.180
nonsensical things?

00:58:06.820 --> 00:58:10.780
Or to weep over all mundane stuff?

00:58:11.500 --> 00:58:12.500
weep

00:58:16.740 --> 00:58:22.420
No, it is to become something that is the instrument,

00:58:22.900 --> 00:58:28.220
to know something that will give you the power.

00:58:28.580 --> 00:58:35.900
This all-pervading power should become your power.

00:58:43.740 --> 00:58:46.300
Power is always connected with violence somehow

00:58:46.660 --> 00:58:50.980
– at this level of human existence.

00:58:53.300 --> 00:58:58.460
But I’m talking of the power of divine love

00:59:02.340 --> 00:59:06.780
that transforms this flower into fruit,

00:59:08.700 --> 00:59:13.900
that has transformed you from amoeba stage to this,

00:59:16.620 --> 00:59:20.060
and that is going to transform you into your state

00:59:20.980 --> 00:59:24.260
of Realization.

00:59:27.420 --> 00:59:31.700
How an egg grows into a bird?

00:59:35.060 --> 00:59:37.460
And how at the right time

00:59:40.820 --> 00:59:43.940
the bird comes completely transformed from

00:59:44.580 --> 00:59:48.620
the ordinary egg?

00:59:52.540 --> 00:59:57.900
This power is the power of Holy Ghost.

00:59:59.620 --> 01:00:04.700
People do not like when I talk about Christ.

01:00:07.060 --> 01:00:10.260
The other day in Belgium a lady asked Me why should

01:00:10.660 --> 01:00:16.060
I talk about Christ in an Indian way?

01:00:22.260 --> 01:00:26.820
I told her, “Was Christ born in Belgium?

01:00:28.420 --> 01:00:32.860
Or was He born a Westerner?”

01:00:34.500 --> 01:00:39.780
Many know that He lived in India and not in England.

01:00:42.460 --> 01:00:45.820
Why, have you taken His contract,

01:00:47.820 --> 01:00:52.780
that you think you know all about Christ?

01:00:54.260 --> 01:00:56.340
You’ll be amazed that about Christ was written

01:00:56.700 --> 01:01:02.380
fourteen thousand years back in India.

01:01:05.100 --> 01:01:11.500
Bible is not enough to contain such a great personality.

01:01:15.300 --> 01:01:17.860
By saying, “We love God, we love Christ

01:01:18.300 --> 01:01:27.140
and Christ is love”, this is all imaginary behavior.

01:01:33.380 --> 01:01:36.500
It’s just a fantasy.

01:01:36.820 --> 01:01:39.260
Reality is that Christ exists within you

01:01:39.580 --> 01:01:44.100
and He is to be awakened within you.

01:01:47.820 --> 01:01:52.460
It is He who said, “You are to be born again.”

01:01:53.180 --> 01:01:56.580
What are we doing about it?

01:01:56.900 --> 01:01:59.660
We call somebody and say, “All right, I’ll baptize

01:01:59.980 --> 01:02:02.460
your child”, artificially you take some water, pour on

01:02:02.820 --> 01:02:06.820
his head and say, “He’s baptized.”

01:02:11.580 --> 01:02:15.060
This is all artificial.

01:02:15.580 --> 01:02:20.500
So, when people get disillusioned from this kind

01:02:20.820 --> 01:02:26.180
of artificial behavior, they fall into another mess.

01:02:32.060 --> 01:02:35.740
You don’t have to go anywhere.

01:02:38.700 --> 01:02:42.580
Your spirit resides within you.

01:02:43.180 --> 01:02:47.620
You don’t have to go to the forest in seeking.

01:02:49.740 --> 01:02:53.540
Your Kundalini is within you.

01:02:54.300 --> 01:02:57.660
Your centers are there.

01:02:58.620 --> 01:03:01.460
The Kundalini will rise and you will become

01:03:01.780 --> 01:03:04.860
Self-realized.

01:03:09.460 --> 01:03:12.260
As an egg becomes the transformed bird,

01:03:12.580 --> 01:03:16.900
you will become the spirit.

01:03:21.380 --> 01:03:24.420
You don’t have to run for it.

01:03:25.820 --> 01:03:28.860
But first thing one must know that we have to know

01:03:29.260 --> 01:03:33.300
all about it, first of all.

01:03:36.100 --> 01:03:39.740
If you are still busy with your reading and busy with

01:03:40.060 --> 01:03:42.220
your ideas and your conditionings,

01:03:42.660 --> 01:03:46.820
it’s not going to work out.

01:03:52.500 --> 01:03:54.620
It’s act better with the people who are simple

01:03:55.060 --> 01:03:58.860
and not so complicated.

01:04:02.060 --> 01:04:05.380
So I would request you to ask Me some questions about it.

01:04:06.060 --> 01:04:09.420
Today is just an introduction I have given you in short.

01:04:09.980 --> 01:04:11.300
You can ask Me questions,

01:04:11.820 --> 01:04:16.100
but the questions should be

01:04:16.940 --> 01:04:21.060
suggestive of your seeking, that would be better.

01:04:43.140 --> 01:04:46.180
If you belong to any cult or any opinion,

01:04:46.500 --> 01:04:47.580
you better think about it –

01:04:48.180 --> 01:04:51.700
what have you got out of it?

01:04:57.940 --> 01:04:58.980
Here I am,

01:04:59.540 --> 01:05:02.300
I am saying that you have to be your spirit and

01:05:02.740 --> 01:05:06.460
can happen through Sahaja Yoga.

01:05:13.220 --> 01:05:16.220
Sahaja means spontaneous happening,

01:05:19.580 --> 01:05:22.700
and yoga is the union.

01:05:23.580 --> 01:05:26.420
And that is what I think we have to achieve,

01:05:26.740 --> 01:05:30.180
and that’s what you want.

01:05:32.660 --> 01:05:35.740
But I’ve seen so many people who come just to

01:05:36.100 --> 01:05:39.740
argue with Me when they haven’t got anything,

01:05:40.060 --> 01:05:45.060
as just like unpaid pleaders,

01:05:50.540 --> 01:05:51.820
because they cannot accept

01:05:52.460 --> 01:05:56.700
that there might have been some mistake.

01:06:00.060 --> 01:06:02.820
Human beings after all, have to make mistakes,

01:06:03.500 --> 01:06:06.820
there’s no wrong in that.

01:06:10.540 --> 01:06:14.620
They should not feel guilty about it.

01:06:15.380 --> 01:06:19.420
They should not feel guilty about anything whatsoever,

01:06:21.660 --> 01:06:24.100
because I’m talking about God,

01:06:24.700 --> 01:06:28.900
who is the ocean of love;

01:06:32.380 --> 01:06:38.060
who is the ocean of compassion;

01:06:40.580 --> 01:06:45.740
who is the ocean of forgiveness.

01:06:46.700 --> 01:06:49.420
But we do not even understand that ocean,

01:06:49.860 --> 01:06:53.380
how great it is.

01:06:55.660 --> 01:06:59.780
How beautifully it cleanses us,

01:07:00.780 --> 01:07:03.060
gives us a nice bath,

01:07:05.220 --> 01:07:09.700
beautifully traps us into nice warmth,

01:07:13.220 --> 01:07:19.340
and takes us to the realm of His kingdom.

01:07:22.500 --> 01:07:26.060
This is happening en masse now.

01:07:28.820 --> 01:07:32.220
It is happening in other countries – specially in India

01:07:32.660 --> 01:07:37.900
thousands of people have got realization in the villages.

01:07:44.460 --> 01:07:47.820
And it should happen to all of you here.

01:07:49.540 --> 01:07:55.900
But if you are not seeking, I cannot force.

01:08:01.260 --> 01:08:04.860
You cannot take the horse, you can take the horse

01:08:05.260 --> 01:08:10.860
up to the river, put his mouth in the river –

01:08:18.060 --> 01:08:19.900
but the horse has to drink the water

01:08:20.420 --> 01:08:24.700
and enjoy the satisfaction.

01:08:31.220 --> 01:08:35.060
This is all your freedom.

01:08:35.820 --> 01:08:39.820
You have to achieve in your freedom.

01:08:41.860 --> 01:08:45.820
We cannot force it on anyone.

01:08:47.140 --> 01:08:55.500
So there is no need for you to be any way aggressive.

01:08:59.660 --> 01:09:02.900
Because even if I want, I may not be able

01:09:03.260 --> 01:09:07.540
to give you Realization.

01:09:11.660 --> 01:09:15.700
It has to work out some time for some people.

01:09:19.460 --> 01:09:21.060
So I have to request you,

01:09:21.740 --> 01:09:26.500
be kind to yourself and fair to yourself.

01:09:28.620 --> 01:09:33.780
You are a seeker and you have to have your Realization.

01:09:37.620 --> 01:09:41.740
And that is why I’m here.

01:09:43.420 --> 01:09:47.140
I have come to give you something.

01:09:48.940 --> 01:09:52.900
That should in no way challenge your ego.

01:09:54.340 --> 01:09:56.580
As I was telling this morning, I don’t understand

01:09:57.140 --> 01:10:00.580
any laws, I do not understand any copyright,

01:10:01.300 --> 01:10:03.380
I do not understand insurance,

01:10:03.980 --> 01:10:07.980
I don’t know how to drive.

01:10:17.900 --> 01:10:21.460
But, one thing I know is Kundalini.

01:10:23.060 --> 01:10:27.660
So you should not feel hurt if I know it,

01:10:29.660 --> 01:10:33.500
but you will know yourself.

01:10:38.700 --> 01:10:43.180
You will be able to do it yourself.

01:10:44.300 --> 01:10:47.420
There’s one person in India who got realization and so

01:10:47.740 --> 01:10:53.660
far he has given realization to ten thousand people.

01:11:00.780 --> 01:11:04.980
Tomorrow I will also tell you how Kundalini awakening,

01:11:05.340 --> 01:11:09.340
as a by-product, manifests the curing of incurable

01:11:09.700 --> 01:11:14.740
diseases like cancer and other diseases.

01:11:23.380 --> 01:11:27.220
How it cures mental diseases and how it takes you out

01:11:27.860 --> 01:11:33.660
of the clutches of your bad habits.

01:11:36.900 --> 01:11:41.340
And how you become your own guru.

01:11:44.100 --> 01:11:46.820
So I would like to have some questions from you.

01:11:47.220 --> 01:11:50.260
If you have to ask any questions, please ask Me,

01:11:50.580 --> 01:11:54.340
without any fear.

01:11:57.620 --> 01:11:59.740
Thank you very much.

01:12:00.380 --> 01:12:02.980
May God bless you.

01:12:29.060 --> 01:12:32.260
Mataji, he asks the difference between Purusha

01:12:32.580 --> 01:12:34.300
in Indian language and the Holy Ghost?

01:12:34.740 --> 01:12:36.380
Purusha?

01:12:57.580 --> 01:13:01.460
Purusha is the God-Almighty.

01:13:01.820 --> 01:13:05.580
Holy Ghost is His power which manifests this Universe

01:13:07.340 --> 01:13:11.500
and is the Kundalini within you.

01:13:24.660 --> 01:13:30.420
That is the Holy Ghost. It’s called as Adi Shakti.

01:13:40.900 --> 01:13:44.060
Adi Shakti means Primordial Power.

01:14:11.220 --> 01:14:17.420
He asks what kind of meditation do you request?

01:14:19.460 --> 01:14:22.460
That I’ll tell you. A good question.

01:14:22.820 --> 01:14:26.060
That’s what I’m going to tell you.

01:14:34.340 --> 01:14:36.460
Mother, he asks about the manifestations when

01:14:36.860 --> 01:14:38.060
the Kundalini rises?

01:14:38.540 --> 01:14:40.540
That I’m going to tell you later on – the whole thing,

01:14:40.860 --> 01:14:44.620
isn’t it, it’s a complete subject which I’ll handle.

01:14:44.980 --> 01:14:47.900
I’m going to be here for three lectures now in Vienna.

01:14:48.420 --> 01:14:51.220
So in one lecture I thought of giving you the introduction,

01:14:51.660 --> 01:14:53.900
and later on I’m definitely going to tell you

01:14:54.300 --> 01:14:59.340
all things about it. Everything. No secrets.

01:14:59.820 --> 01:15:01.100
He asks what do you feel physically when the Kundalini rises?

01:15:01.860 --> 01:15:04.100
That I will tell, just now, I will tell.

01:15:06.900 --> 01:15:09.620
That the first time you feel the all-Pervading power

01:15:10.060 --> 01:15:13.700
as cool breeze of the Holy Ghost.

01:15:18.980 --> 01:15:22.980
Coming out of your head also.

01:15:24.740 --> 01:15:30.060
And in your fingers, you start feeling it all around you.

01:15:36.580 --> 01:15:39.660
He asks what happens with the breathing and with the heart?

01:15:40.460 --> 01:15:44.140
You become very normal.

01:15:48.460 --> 01:15:49.900
He tells it’s not the Kundalini then.

01:15:50.380 --> 01:15:53.820
Why, what should happen, you should die?

01:15:54.380 --> 01:15:56.740
You have read something, now you see for yourself.

01:15:57.260 --> 01:15:59.260
Reading is not the way to get convinced,

01:15:59.500 --> 01:16:02.940
is a mediocracy.

01:16:09.060 --> 01:16:10.900
You may go on reading thousands of books;

01:16:11.300 --> 01:16:14.860
you cannot get your realization from books.

01:16:28.060 --> 01:16:29.260
Mother, do You believe that

01:16:29.620 --> 01:16:32.060
we don’t need a guru in general?

01:16:39.620 --> 01:16:42.100
No, you do need a guru – in the sense that

01:16:42.500 --> 01:16:47.460
an enlightened light can only enlighten another light.

01:16:52.300 --> 01:16:53.860
But where are the real gurus?

01:16:54.140 --> 01:16:56.260
They are all hiding in the Himalayas or some

01:16:56.700 --> 01:16:58.700
other places, and when I tell them, they say,

01:16:58.940 --> 01:17:00.500
“We are not interested in these people,

01:17:00.900 --> 01:17:04.180
they are not seekers.”

01:17:12.700 --> 01:17:15.540
The only people who are interested in your purses

01:17:15.820 --> 01:17:20.100
are down here, in the market.

01:17:24.620 --> 01:17:31.300
With great persuasion I sent one guru to America,

01:17:31.780 --> 01:17:33.260
who returned within three days.

01:17:33.580 --> 01:17:35.060
He said, “I had enough of these Americans –

01:17:35.540 --> 01:17:38.780
horrible people.

01:17:45.820 --> 01:17:47.380
They only understand dollars,

01:17:47.700 --> 01:17:49.460
they don’t want to have Reality.

