They have no time for that.”

01:18:23.620 --> 01:18:27.500
Mother, he asks if to get Realization is only possible

01:18:27.940 --> 01:18:31.300
after certain meditation, or if you can prepare

01:18:31.620 --> 01:18:34.060
the people to get this experience?

01:18:35.180 --> 01:18:38.060
If you are a human being, you can get Realization.

01:18:38.420 --> 01:18:39.740
You are already prepared

01:18:40.060 --> 01:18:43.060
because you are a human being.

01:18:52.780 --> 01:18:55.900
But if your human sustenance is little bit spoiled,

01:18:56.300 --> 01:18:58.300
then the Kundalini, though it comes up, it may go down

01:18:58.540 --> 01:19:03.700
a little, come up a little, and it will establish itself.

01:19:33.980 --> 01:19:35.980
Mother, he doesn’t understand how he comes to

01:19:36.300 --> 01:19:38.740
the spontaneous experience?

01:19:39.860 --> 01:19:41.580
He thinks, he has to meditate, or something.

01:19:42.100 --> 01:19:44.340
You cannot meditate, you go into meditation.

01:19:44.660 --> 01:19:46.660
That’s very simple, I’ll tell you what happens really.

01:19:47.100 --> 01:19:49.660
You have to put your hands towards Me like this.

01:19:50.140 --> 01:19:52.580
How you see the [tree] leaves become green,

01:19:52.900 --> 01:19:56.340
in the same way you put your hands towards Me,

01:19:57.260 --> 01:20:02.500
and as I am a Realized Soul, the information goes

01:20:02.740 --> 01:20:04.940
through these fingers.

01:20:05.300 --> 01:20:07.660
Through them the information goes to the Kundalini,

01:20:08.100 --> 01:20:10.980
and She rises. Spontaneously.

01:20:11.300 --> 01:20:15.620
Like the Mother Earth, when you put the seed

01:20:15.900 --> 01:20:18.100
in the Mother Earth, the seed knows it’s

01:20:18.340 --> 01:20:21.540
the Mother Earth and the primule –

01:20:22.060 --> 01:20:27.780
the germinating power – arises by itself.

01:20:46.260 --> 01:20:49.540
Then you are in meditation, you don’t have to do

01:20:49.780 --> 01:20:53.900
meditation, you are in meditation.

01:21:04.540 --> 01:21:06.100
When it is obstructed in some people,

01:21:06.580 --> 01:21:08.500
you can see with the naked eye the pulsation

01:21:08.820 --> 01:21:13.180
of the Kundalini at the sacrum bone.

01:21:18.140 --> 01:21:21.180
You can hear the rising of the Kundalini

01:21:21.620 --> 01:21:24.060
with the stethoscope, even you can see with your

01:21:24.420 --> 01:21:28.740
naked eyes if there is obstruction.

01:21:33.300 --> 01:21:35.660
When She crosses this Agnya Chakra, then you become

01:21:35.980 --> 01:21:38.420
thoughtlessly aware.

01:21:38.660 --> 01:21:43.060
You are aware, but there is no thought.

01:21:49.500 --> 01:21:51.580
There are many who talk about thoughtless awareness,

01:21:52.180 --> 01:21:56.140
but they never achieve it.

01:21:58.940 --> 01:22:02.180
Then you go beyond, when it comes onto the head here,

01:22:02.500 --> 01:22:06.620
you feel the throbbing on your head here.

01:22:11.660 --> 01:22:13.900
And then you start feeling the cool breeze coming

01:22:14.220 --> 01:22:17.300
out of your head.

01:22:20.980 --> 01:22:23.700
We must know that what we can do like jumping,

01:22:24.060 --> 01:22:29.460
doing all other things, can be done by everyone.

01:22:33.740 --> 01:22:39.980
But the living force does something that we cannot do.

01:22:42.260 --> 01:22:44.820
We cannot make the cool breeze come out of our head,

01:22:44.820 --> 01:22:46.740
can we?

01:22:52.180 --> 01:22:54.980
And you are not to be satisfied,

01:22:55.300 --> 01:22:57.100
give a false certificate about it;

01:22:57.420 --> 01:23:01.340
you have to certify yourself.

01:23:07.260 --> 01:23:11.060
Then your fingers are enlightened.

01:23:13.380 --> 01:23:15.620
Because these are the seven centers – five, six

01:23:15.940 --> 01:23:18.940
and seven.

01:23:21.620 --> 01:23:26.220
About which I’ll tell you tomorrow in details.

01:23:28.220 --> 01:23:31.900
They will all get enlightened.

01:23:32.860 --> 01:23:35.460
And from the fingers like this you can make out

01:23:35.700 --> 01:23:39.780
what chakra of a person is catching.

01:23:44.940 --> 01:23:46.780
If the left side is catching that means there’s

01:23:47.060 --> 01:23:48.580
an emotional problem;

01:23:49.060 --> 01:23:50.580
if the right side is catching means there’s physical

01:23:51.180 --> 01:23:54.300
or mental problem.

01:24:04.980 --> 01:24:07.300
Then you can also know the permutations and

01:24:07.620 --> 01:24:14.580
combinations which are decoded, you can verify them.

01:24:16.660 --> 01:24:19.380
Sitting down here you can find out about anyone,

01:24:19.700 --> 01:24:21.940
even the dead people –

01:24:22.580 --> 01:24:26.820
were they realized or not?

01:24:34.980 --> 01:24:38.580
If they were realized you will start getting a cool breeze.

01:24:39.060 --> 01:24:42.820
That’s the rapport established with the Divine.

01:24:47.660 --> 01:24:51.860
Any absolute question you ask – and if it is the answer

01:24:52.220 --> 01:24:58.260
is ‘yes’ – then you get a cool breeze flowing.

01:25:03.060 --> 01:25:08.820
If somebody is a false person, you get burnings.

01:25:10.780 --> 01:25:14.260
If he’s a evil genius, you might get even blisters,

01:25:14.580 --> 01:25:16.220
little bit.

01:25:21.340 --> 01:25:25.300
If somebody is going to die, then you get numbness

01:25:25.620 --> 01:25:27.060
on the fingers.

01:25:27.420 --> 01:25:28.820
If somebody is going to die, then you get

01:25:29.260 --> 01:25:32.380
numbness on the fingers.

01:25:37.620 --> 01:25:39.860
So once you know about the chakras, then you have

01:25:40.220 --> 01:25:44.300
to know how to correct it.

01:25:49.540 --> 01:25:54.060
All this knowledge is your own,

01:25:55.700 --> 01:25:59.060
and is to be given to you.

01:26:00.500 --> 01:26:03.580
It has to be all free, as I said.

01:26:04.700 --> 01:26:07.980
Has to be all free, as I said.

01:26:09.540 --> 01:26:15.620
It is, I would say, I’m like a cashier in the bank.

01:26:18.340 --> 01:26:22.060
And I am just giving you what you have got already

01:26:22.380 --> 01:26:25.460
within yourself.

01:26:27.860 --> 01:26:30.380
Also the knowledge to know the things that

01:26:31.220 --> 01:26:34.340
you have got.

01:26:38.140 --> 01:26:41.940
And how to use them.

01:26:44.380 --> 01:26:45.700
It cannot be believed that there

01:26:46.060 --> 01:26:50.820
could be someone like that.

01:26:51.620 --> 01:26:58.420
There have been many more like this - I am One of them.

01:27:02.180 --> 01:27:03.060
May God bless you.

01:27:09.260 --> 01:27:11.700
Which kind of religion do you have, Mother?

01:27:12.220 --> 01:27:16.700
Is the religion of all the religions.

01:27:17.140 --> 01:27:21.180
Because it’s the essence of everything.

01:27:21.740 --> 01:27:28.260
Actually all the religions started with life’s force only.

01:27:32.500 --> 01:27:34.740
All the incarnations and prophets were true

01:27:35.100 --> 01:27:38.180
and all connected.

01:27:42.140 --> 01:27:45.340
Absolute concord.

01:27:47.260 --> 01:27:50.540
And it’s such a coordinated thing within ourselves

01:27:50.900 --> 01:27:54.260
and they are placed within ourselves.

01:27:57.380 --> 01:28:01.700
But all these beautiful flowers which grew onto

01:28:02.060 --> 01:28:04.260
the Tree of Life were taken away by each one of them,

01:28:04.820 --> 01:28:09.980
and they have said, “This is mine, this is mine.”

01:28:16.220 --> 01:28:21.220
The flowers are dead and ugly.

