Mataji, many of us have learned that it is extremely

01:28:33.460 --> 01:28:36.300
dangerous to wake up this Kundalini,

01:28:36.660 --> 01:28:38.140
I’m sure You know this.

01:28:38.580 --> 01:28:40.340
Yes, yes, they all say so.

01:28:40.820 --> 01:28:43.220
That’s the only escape they can have, My child.

01:28:43.660 --> 01:28:45.580
That’s the only escape they can have.

