01:29:53.300 --> 01:29:57.580
No that is Adi Bhautik. Parapsychology.

01:29:58.100 --> 01:30:00.700
The parapsychology has to deal with Adi Bhautik,

01:30:00.940 --> 01:30:06.260
is the left side, the collective subconscious.

01:30:09.260 --> 01:30:11.820
You cannot explain anything, what you are doing,

01:30:12.180 --> 01:30:14.620
you see, you are flying in the air, what you are doing,

01:30:14.860 --> 01:30:19.540
you don’t know. How you are curing, you don’t know.

01:30:22.980 --> 01:30:25.980
You are blind.

01:30:27.500 --> 01:30:31.860
But in Sahaja Yoga, even a child knows.

01:30:34.540 --> 01:30:38.140
If he’s a born-realized, he knows.

01:30:41.340 --> 01:30:45.060
He knows what chakras people are catching.

01:30:47.380 --> 01:30:50.820
If they are very highly Self-realized souls, they also

01:30:51.180 --> 01:30:54.260
know about Kundalini.

01:30:57.060 --> 01:30:59.300
There are many children these days born

01:30:59.660 --> 01:31:03.100
who are realized souls.

01:31:06.300 --> 01:31:08.900
But those who are not realized are the parents,

01:31:09.220 --> 01:31:13.300
and they don’t understand their children.

01:31:16.260 --> 01:31:18.660
Great saints are taking their birth on this earth

01:31:19.060 --> 01:31:21.380
these days.

01:31:24.700 --> 01:31:30.460
Till you get Realization, you won’t understand them.

