is better, in My speech I will give you answers about it,

01:34:28.100 --> 01:34:33.260
but moreover it’s the ocean of knowledge.

01:34:40.700 --> 01:34:42.180
When you will yourself have the light,

01:34:42.620 --> 01:34:45.740
you can see through, yourself.

