01:37:08.660 --> 01:37:10.580
You see, just because of reading a book,

01:37:10.940 --> 01:37:13.820
are you satisfied, my child? You are a seeker,

01:37:14.220 --> 01:37:16.460
why should you be satisfied with a book?

01:37:16.700 --> 01:37:18.780
Why don’t you see for yourself?

01:37:19.060 --> 01:37:22.060
Again I’ve said, just a book he has bought,

01:37:22.300 --> 01:37:24.700
and he is wasting everybody’s time for one book.

01:37:25.060 --> 01:37:30.420
He has done no good to anyone.

