01:41:13.260 --> 01:41:16.420
It means ‘twice-born’.

01:41:17.940 --> 01:41:21.860
First the bird comes out of the egg, then it tries

01:41:22.180 --> 01:41:26.940
to fly a little bit, and ultimately

01:41:27.620 --> 01:41:31.100
it receives the power and it gets confident and it

01:41:31.540 --> 01:41:35.860
spreads its wings around.

01:41:47.140 --> 01:41:50.940
But in the beginning, the mother bird looks after

01:41:51.380 --> 01:41:55.180
the baby bird.

01:41:58.260 --> 01:42:02.980
She hides behind and calls the little bird

01:42:03.300 --> 01:42:08.180
so the little bird takes the courage to fly.

01:42:12.860 --> 01:42:17.420
And that’s how it works out.

