01:45:26.260 --> 01:45:27.740
he can go away, or if he has to sit here,

01:45:28.180 --> 01:45:30.060
you better put your hands like this.

01:45:30.380 --> 01:45:34.940
Because those who are adamant spoil the vibrations of others.

