01:46:44.500 --> 01:46:46.860
Be comfortable.

01:46:49.820 --> 01:46:52.260
Don’t put in any effort, please.

01:46:57.500 --> 01:47:00.500
Just keep your eyes shut, that’s important.

01:47:03.820 --> 01:47:08.300
Because when the Kundalini rises above your Agnya,

01:47:08.620 --> 01:47:13.540
if the eyes are open, it will be hindered.

01:47:26.340 --> 01:47:28.420
Now few instructions I’ll give you

01:47:28.780 --> 01:47:31.140
how to raise your Kundalini.

01:47:37.820 --> 01:47:40.580
But don’t open your eyes.

01:47:44.940 --> 01:47:46.380
Put your left hand towards Me

01:47:46.660 --> 01:47:48.420
and right hand on your heart.

01:47:54.620 --> 01:47:57.540
The hand towards Me should be on your lap,

01:47:57.940 --> 01:48:00.740
the way it was before.

01:48:03.180 --> 01:48:07.220
On your lap, upward.

01:48:11.180 --> 01:48:13.780
Now putting the hand on the spirit

01:48:14.980 --> 01:48:17.340
you ask a question in your heart,

01:48:18.060 --> 01:48:23.380
“Mother, am I the spirit?”

01:48:31.300 --> 01:48:34.820
Ask it thrice.

01:48:42.540 --> 01:48:46.540
What are you feeling?

01:48:54.860 --> 01:49:01.900
Please put your right hand at the left side of your neck,

01:49:03.260 --> 01:49:05.660
right hand.

01:49:12.180 --> 01:49:14.500
From the front.

01:49:18.860 --> 01:49:21.420
Again say it.

01:49:32.220 --> 01:49:35.900
Now, this is the problem of the West, all the time,

01:49:36.420 --> 01:49:40.820
I find people feel guilty for nothing at all.

01:49:54.700 --> 01:49:56.740
And say in your heart,

01:49:57.580 --> 01:50:03.060
“Mother, I am not guilty.”

01:50:12.860 --> 01:50:18.980
Just say it eight times that, “Mother, I am not guilty.”

01:50:46.540 --> 01:50:51.060
Now put the hand down below, on the stomach

01:50:55.900 --> 01:51:01.700
and ask a question, “Mother, am I my own guru?”

01:51:05.060 --> 01:51:08.820
Ask ten times.

01:51:10.180 --> 01:51:14.100
Put the right hand on your stomach

01:51:15.220 --> 01:51:20.140
and ask a question, “Mother am I my own guru?”

01:51:35.860 --> 01:51:37.940
Left hand towards Me

01:51:44.300 --> 01:51:46.780
and on the stomach

01:51:47.180 --> 01:51:48.220
and ask the question,

01:51:48.660 --> 01:51:52.860
“Mother am I my own guru?”

01:51:54.700 --> 01:52:00.780
Left hand should be kept on the lap. Where is your lap?

01:52:04.340 --> 01:52:08.180
Ask the question ten times. Say loudly.

01:52:09.180 --> 01:52:14.820
“Mother am I my own guru?”

01:52:19.060 --> 01:52:25.660
Now just raise the hand again to your heart,

01:52:28.780 --> 01:52:33.540
and say, “Mother I am the spirit.”

01:52:42.220 --> 01:52:47.060
Say it twelve times.

01:52:48.580 --> 01:52:52.460
This is the number of sub-plexuses we have.

01:53:01.500 --> 01:53:04.780
“Mother, I am the spirit.”

01:53:35.620 --> 01:53:38.700
Now put this hand again at the neck and say thrice,

01:53:39.420 --> 01:53:45.420
“Mother I am not guilty.”

01:53:49.900 --> 01:53:52.900
This is very important.

01:54:00.660 --> 01:54:05.220
Now put the right hand across your forehead.

01:54:09.900 --> 01:54:15.260
Now you have to say, “Mother I forgive everyone,

01:54:18.260 --> 01:54:23.820
with your heart, with honesty you say it twice.

01:54:34.660 --> 01:54:38.060
Now put the hand on top of your head,

01:54:38.540 --> 01:54:48.260
touching in the center with your fingers,

01:54:49.060 --> 01:54:52.740
where you had the soft bone,

01:54:53.340 --> 01:54:57.060
and move it clockwise.

01:54:57.500 --> 01:55:03.740
Move your scalp clockwise, backwards and forwards.

01:55:10.540 --> 01:55:12.540
Now raise your hand and see

01:55:12.540 --> 01:55:15.980
if there’s a cool breeze coming in.

01:55:33.140 --> 01:55:35.060
What’s it?

01:55:37.580 --> 01:55:39.980
Higher. Higher.

01:55:55.860 --> 01:55:57.300
Better.

01:55:58.420 --> 01:56:00.820
Warm. It’s hot.

01:56:01.420 --> 01:56:05.220
So now you put your left hand on top of your head …

01:56:10.060 --> 01:56:13.300
and see if it is cool.

01:56:18.980 --> 01:56:20.300
Better.

01:56:34.220 --> 01:56:37.460
Again raise your right hand

01:56:39.340 --> 01:56:41.580
and put the left hand on the liver.

01:56:42.100 --> 01:56:45.300
Put your right hand on the head.

01:56:48.380 --> 01:56:50.140
Liver.

01:56:57.060 --> 01:56:59.340
Left hand on the liver. That’s wrong.

01:57:01.100 --> 01:57:02.900
Good.

01:57:10.340 --> 01:57:12.980
Put them left to the right now if you can.

01:57:13.660 --> 01:57:15.340
Put them left to the right.

01:57:15.700 --> 01:57:18.220
If you can put them left to the right.

01:57:18.620 --> 01:57:21.260
And then raise it. Left to the right, left to the right.

01:57:23.060 --> 01:57:24.620
That’s all right.

01:57:26.140 --> 01:57:29.660
Now see if there’s a cool breeze coming in.

01:57:37.780 --> 01:57:40.620
Ah, better.

01:57:49.100 --> 01:57:51.660
Now put both the hands towards Me.

01:57:57.660 --> 01:58:02.260
Now see if there’s cool breeze coming in your hands.

01:58:09.420 --> 01:58:11.300
Just see it.

01:58:11.700 --> 01:58:14.060
You go round.

01:58:34.860 --> 01:58:36.780
All right?

01:58:39.220 --> 01:58:41.460
See if he can feel it?

01:58:54.580 --> 01:58:59.260
Lower. Press it hard. Press it hard.

01:59:14.300 --> 01:59:19.700
Just feel his head. Ask him to be comfortable.

01:59:27.340 --> 01:59:30.620
Please don’t feel guilty.

01:59:31.060 --> 01:59:33.820
It will work out.

02:00:25.180 --> 02:00:28.860
How is it? Started?

02:02:04.060 --> 02:02:06.420
Hah. Right.

02:02:13.340 --> 02:02:16.940
Don’t think about it. It starts working.

02:02:17.500 --> 02:02:19.180
The cool breeze is coming out of many people.

02:02:19.620 --> 02:02:23.860
Just see your, raise your hand and see for yourself.

02:02:29.060 --> 02:02:32.060
Say that the cool breeze is coming out of your head

02:02:32.620 --> 02:02:36.660
in many people and see for yourself.

02:02:46.780 --> 02:02:49.820
And don’t think about it.

02:03:33.980 --> 02:03:34.980
Right.

02:03:47.380 --> 02:03:55.540
Shri Mataji sends cool breeze through the microphone

02:05:04.820 --> 02:05:06.860
Its better now.

02:05:46.860 --> 02:05:50.740
First you will feel it on top of your head,

02:05:51.180 --> 02:05:54.180
and then you will feel it on your fingertips,

02:05:54.620 --> 02:05:57.980
as you’ll be growing.

02:06:03.420 --> 02:06:06.780
But some of you might feel both the things.

02:06:14.060 --> 02:06:16.300
They’re feeling it?

02:06:51.700 --> 02:06:53.500
Better?

02:06:54.260 --> 02:06:57.180
Better now?

02:07:28.380 --> 02:07:33.140
Put it on the heart.

02:07:34.740 --> 02:07:39.500
Little higher. Press it hard.

02:08:47.060 --> 02:08:49.660
This side. Move it in the center of the heart.

02:08:50.540 --> 02:08:54.980
In the center, in the center of the heart, this side,

02:08:55.660 --> 02:09:01.540
in the center heart. Press it hard.

02:09:20.060 --> 02:09:21.380
Put it at the Kundalini.

02:09:21.700 --> 02:09:25.420
Put your hand at the Kundalini. Press it hard.

02:09:25.820 --> 02:09:30.140
Little higher. Like that.

02:09:34.900 --> 02:09:38.460
Place the other hand like that outside.

02:09:43.700 --> 02:09:45.740
Left Swadhisthana.

02:10:07.460 --> 02:10:10.220
Right Swadhisthana.

02:11:04.820 --> 02:11:06.620
Some of you have to say again that,

02:11:06.940 --> 02:11:09.780
“Mother, I am not guilty.”

02:11:14.420 --> 02:11:15.660
Now you have to say,

02:11:16.060 --> 02:11:19.340
“Mother, please give me my realization.”

02:11:26.540 --> 02:11:30.620
You have to ask because I cannot overcome your freedom.

02:11:54.420 --> 02:11:56.540
Right heart.

02:11:59.140 --> 02:12:02.220
Ask seven times please.

02:13:48.740 --> 02:13:50.420
Once you feel the cool breeze you’ll tie up …

02:13:50.900 --> 02:13:54.100
all the Sahaja yogis should tie them up.

02:15:19.140 --> 02:15:21.580
Those who are feeling the cool breeze over their head,

02:15:21.820 --> 02:15:26.380
please raise your hands, all of you.

02:15:31.620 --> 02:15:33.860
You can see for yourself.

02:15:47.300 --> 02:15:49.980
Just move your hand up and down.

02:16:10.300 --> 02:16:12.380
He’s got it.

02:16:21.060 --> 02:16:23.740
Raise your hand if you have got cool breeze in the hand.

02:16:29.700 --> 02:16:31.820
Raise them.

02:16:34.260 --> 02:16:38.740
Got it? Horrible. But it will go out.

02:16:40.180 --> 02:16:42.780
You’ll have to give up that man.

02:16:45.780 --> 02:16:48.140
But to keep it up and to establish it

02:16:48.580 --> 02:16:51.340
you have to listen to us.

02:16:58.060 --> 02:17:00.460
You have got it because of your seeking

02:17:03.900 --> 02:17:07.060
but it will go down

02:17:09.260 --> 02:17:12.420
in case you have problems

02:17:16.940 --> 02:17:21.300
or you are doing things which should not be done.

02:17:23.220 --> 02:17:26.860
So please listen to us.

02:17:28.780 --> 02:17:30.540
Again tomorrow please come

02:17:33.940 --> 02:17:38.060
and you’ll grow more

02:17:43.340 --> 02:17:48.420
and you will find the difference tomorrow again.

02:17:51.260 --> 02:17:56.220
You must take out everything that is in your neck in the night.

02:17:58.420 --> 02:18:01.420
Take out your watches.

02:18:01.980 --> 02:18:05.100
Place yourself free.

02:18:08.900 --> 02:18:12.060
And they will give you the photograph.

02:18:12.460 --> 02:18:14.820
Have you got? Today?

02:18:16.060 --> 02:18:19.980
All right, tomorrow they’ll give you the photograph.

02:18:23.820 --> 02:18:28.180
And tomorrow again we have to re-establish.

02:18:35.220 --> 02:18:39.900
Please don’t think about it and discuss it.

02:18:44.780 --> 02:18:48.500
It is beyond thought.

02:18:50.580 --> 02:18:54.060
Maintain your peaceful behavior.

02:19:01.180 --> 02:19:04.540
May God bless you.

02:19:06.300 --> 02:19:10.660
I will teach you now how to raise your Kundalini.

02:19:15.340 --> 02:19:19.140
Get your eyes open.

02:19:32.580 --> 02:19:38.140
You put your hand in the centre of Kundalini, left hand.

02:19:40.940 --> 02:19:45.500
And now start rolling, your right hand.

02:19:46.180 --> 02:19:49.420
This is the hand of your action.

02:19:50.980 --> 02:19:55.540
This way. Take it forward, downward,

02:19:55.900 --> 02:19:58.100
backwards and upwards.

02:20:03.780 --> 02:20:06.940
Now put up your hands as much as you can

02:20:07.500 --> 02:20:11.780
and give it a knot, to your Kundalini.

02:20:13.500 --> 02:20:15.700
That’s the first time.

02:20:17.620 --> 02:20:21.060
Now take another, awakening.

02:20:21.740 --> 02:20:23.860
Move your hand again the same way slowly.

02:20:24.500 --> 02:20:26.060
Your hand will roll itself.

02:20:26.860 --> 02:20:29.940
When it is cleared out it will move much faster,

02:20:30.620 --> 02:20:33.180
but do not force it.

02:20:34.100 --> 02:20:37.540
Now take it on top of your head and give it one knot,

02:20:37.540 --> 02:20:38.540
slowly, turn it quite a lot

02:20:39.060 --> 02:20:42.220
and give it a knot and take it down.

02:20:46.220 --> 02:20:47.900
Now take another one.

02:20:48.380 --> 02:20:51.580
This is the last and the third one.

02:20:59.260 --> 02:21:05.380
Now take your hands as far as possible and give a big...

02:21:05.380 --> 02:21:07.820
Now do tie these knots -

02:21:08.300 --> 02:21:16.540
one, two and three and bring down.

02:21:20.260 --> 02:21:23.140
Do your hands like this.

02:21:23.820 --> 02:21:27.380
Throw away everything and now see.

02:21:29.540 --> 02:21:33.500
Now see the flow in the hands.

02:21:36.340 --> 02:21:39.340
Feeling the cool breeze?

02:21:42.140 --> 02:21:44.780
Some of you will definitely feel it.

02:21:53.940 --> 02:21:57.180
You’ll feel very peaceful, comfortable,

02:21:57.700 --> 02:22:00.380
and you’ll sleep very well.

02:22:05.340 --> 02:22:07.100
Wear plain clothes,

02:22:07.620 --> 02:22:10.140
loose clothes in the night

02:22:10.540 --> 02:22:14.580
loose clothes and plain; plain; means not colored

02:22:22.940 --> 02:22:26.940
and when you come tomorrow, don’t discuss it.

02:22:28.140 --> 02:22:33.940
I’m here for two days and I’m sure I’ll establish it before going.

02:22:43.500 --> 02:22:45.220
I have to make a humble request,

02:22:45.660 --> 02:22:47.780
to people who are wearing orange clothes and all that

02:22:48.180 --> 02:22:51.900
please take them out.

02:23:06.180 --> 02:23:08.180
If time comes tomorrow I’ll tell you the secret

02:23:08.620 --> 02:23:12.140
of that also.

02:23:13.260 --> 02:23:17.420
Listen to Me for six-seven days when you with Me.

02:23:30.980 --> 02:23:33.780
I’m your Mother and I’ve come here to tell you

02:23:34.220 --> 02:23:38.660
something that is the Truth.

02:23:41.660 --> 02:23:44.700
So just listen to Me, wear simple dresses,

02:23:45.060 --> 02:23:49.740
tomorrow come in a simple dress, not tight dresses,

02:23:50.180 --> 02:23:52.620
so that Kundalini is easily...

02:24:00.780 --> 02:24:03.100
Something normal, wear something normal,

02:24:03.100 --> 02:24:06.140
whatever is normal for Vienna people,

02:24:06.820 --> 02:24:09.500
they should wear that way.

02:24:11.220 --> 02:24:14.140
Nothing abnormal.

02:24:14.660 --> 02:24:18.220
May God bless you.
